<h2>Using the Geocaches page</h2>
<h3><a name="FindingGeocaches">How to find geocaches on the map</a></h3>
<p>Log in and click the GeoCaches tab. Enter the postcode of, or scroll to the area you want to find caches. The closest 20 will appear on the map. To get the details, click on the cache.</p>
